    7         9        5          17           5      5
[xxxxxxx][xxxxxxxxx][xxxxx][xxxxxxxxxxxxxxx][xxxxx][xxxxx]
  CCL ID   DCCL ID   FLAGS   TIME SINCE DAY   SRC   DEST

7+9+5+17+5+5 = 6 bytes

new class -> message_head
message -> message_body

both classes own message_var, which can be subclassed into

int,static,hex,bool,float,string
time,source,destination

